title: Evangeline Lilly was in no hurry to lose post-baby weight
body:
Evangeline Lilly was in no hurry to lose post-baby weight

Los Angeles:

Evangeline Lilly took two years to lose the weight she put on during her pregnancy and the actor says she has no qualms about it.

The 38-year-old actor said she was “patient” with her post-baby body and wanted to be healthy to nurse her children.

“You see those headlines that say, ‘I lost my baby weight in three months!’ And I used to read that and I would think, why would you want…

Maisie Williams bids adieu to ‘Game of Thrones’

London:

Maisie Williams has completed the shooting of the last season of “Game of Thrones” and the actor raised a toast to her journey in the hit epic fantasy series.

The 21-year-old actor, who is known for playing Arya Stark in the HBO series, took to Instagram to say goodbye to the show on which she has worked since its premiere in 2011.

“Goodbye Belfast. Goodbye Arya. Goodbye ‘Game of…

summary: Alright now that I’ve calmed down I don’t think Maisie’s giving spoilers like that, because if she’s doing it without realising...
body:
Alright now that I’ve calmed down I don’t think Maisie’s giving spoilers like that, because if she’s doing it without realising at least Lena wouldn’t join in, there’s honestly no way they would let them do it.

So I reckon they are soft-trolling. But that has to mean like she’s standing among the fallen ones in her final scene, right? With the blood and everything, it has to mean that she’s in a battle/ murder spree of some sort. Does that mean she’s the only one standing among the list of people she intended to kill? It can’t be that she’s the only Stark alive though. God I want ANSWERS
